message.text:
Hello, everyone! Please join the ITHM Student Council, Marketing and Content Department under Press Relations Officer 

If you join the Marketing and Content Department under the Press Relations Officer, you won’t just get to explore your creativity, improve your writing, and sharpen your skills in content creation and publicity.

You’ll also have ME as your Director! 😉
And that means you’ll have someone who’s ready to guide you, hype you up, and make sure that your experience here will be both fun and meaningful.

✅ A platform to share your ideas
✅ Creativity at its best
✅ Memories to treasure
✅ Opportunities to grow your confidence 

So, why wait? This is your sign to take the leap and join us. 😊🩷

message.text:
Hello, everyone! Please join the ITHM Student Council, Marketing and Content Department under Press Relations Officer 

If you join the Marketing and Content Department under the Press Relations Officer, you won’t just get to explore your creativity, improve your writing, and sharpen your skills in content creation and publicity.

You’ll also have ME as your Director! 😉
And that means you’ll have someone who’s ready to guide you, hype you up, and make sure that your experience here will be both fun and meaningful.

✅ A platform to share your ideas
✅ Creativity at its best
✅ Memories to treasure
✅ Opportunities to grow your confidence 

So, why wait? This is your sign to take the leap and join us. 😊🩷

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil
